title: Seamus Kennedy - Comic Irish Drinking Songs
description:
Seamus Kennedy is currently  and by a huge measure the most popular touring Irish folk act in America today. While he does perform and record serious songs, he is most famous for his comedic ones, especially:

The three minute Hamlet
Fishing for Chickens
Armed Forces Tribute (play this for servicemen (they'll piss themselves dry)
Old MacDonald's deformed farm, and
Monkey Farts

He has released several albums, of which I have two commercial ones. I also have several bootlegs and mixed quality mp3s I got from WinMX and other P2P services. Some of these are of decent to poor quality. Don't leave comments telling me that, I already know. I am hoping that someone else will see this torrent and decide to up all the other commercial albums. This is seriously funny stuff. 

American downloaders - Check his website to see when he will next perform in your area. I promise that this guy will not disappoint if you go to see him live. One warning - he really hates Yankee fans.

Seamus' website - http://www.mcnote.com/seamus/
